:::'''Dahao:''' I always feel like we're missing something here at the Realm-Keeping Commission Chancery, but I can never remember what. You've come at just the right time &mdash; help me rule out some possibilities. Say, tell me, what do you think our office is missing?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: 502020101_Option-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: 502020101_Option-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Promo materials showcasing the work of the Realm-Keeping Commission.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020103-->
::::'''Dahao:''' Not that...
::::'''Dahao:''' I raised this with Jingyan before, whether we should be better at promoting how good the Realm-Keeping Commission Chancery is at what it does. But she gave me a list of all the things we've done recently, and there isn't really anything to be proud of.
::::'''Dahao:''' Once we crack a major case that even the Ten-Lords Commission can't solve, then I'll let the whole Exalting Sanctum know about how great the Realm-Keeping Commission is... Until then, we'll keep things on the down-low.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Small ornaments that make this place feel alive.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020107-->
::::'''Dahao:''' Make the place feel alive... Actually, I've thought about that.
::::'''Dahao:''' I'm a big fan of alcoholic nectar and once stashed two bottles of Nectar of Willow Woods at the Chancery, but Officer Jingyan threw them out. She said this is the workplace and it would be undignified if anyone found out.
::::'''Dahao:''' I also like pretty foxian actresses, so I've put up a couple of their pictures on my desk to perk up my spirits. But Officer Jingyan confiscated those too. She said this is the workplace and those images are indecent.
::::'''Dahao:''' *sigh* The only way the Realm-Keeping Commission feels alive is through all the courier parcels on the ground.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} A Realm-Keeping Commission Officer who is actually productive at work.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020112-->
::::'''Dahao:''' {{MC|f=Young lady|m=Young man}}, that remark is uncalled for. At least Officer Jingyan is doing her work. As long as Officer Jingyan is here, then the Realm-Keeping Commission lives up to its name.
::::'''Dahao:''' That Songyan kid may be lazy, but he's smart. I have high hopes for his future.
::::'''Dahao:''' Naturally, if anything actually happens to Exalting Sanctum, you'll find me to be an extremely reliable officer.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is now really the time to be thinking about that?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502020116-->
::::'''Dahao:''' Yeah, I can't figure it out even if I rack my brain. I think I'll play a few rounds of Celestial Jade after work and think it through then.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502020101_10-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502020101_10-->
::::'''Dahao:''' Alright, let's get down to business. {{MC|f=Young lady|m=Young man}}, what do you want?
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
