:{{DIcon|undefined}} When I was dealing with the mara-struck, I found this...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 202010361: Config/Level/Mission/2020103/Act/Act202010361.json-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 202010301--> and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 202010301-->)
:{{DIcon|undefined}} I heard you require my assistance?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 202010301: Config/Level/Mission/2020103/Act/Act202010301.json-->
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 101 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 101 f.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' Oh, that's right! Forgive my forgetfulness &mdash; glad you came, (Trailblazer)! It's great to have one of the general's distinguished guests helping us out.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 102.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' My Realm-Keeping Commission colleagues failed to provide adequate care for the Dragon Lady. I'd like to thank you on behalf of all of them for rescuing her back in Exalting Sanctum Plaza.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} All in a day's work.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's cut to the chase, shall we?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202160006-->
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 103.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' As I'm sure you're aware, symptoms of mara have been spreading ever since the Stellaron incident occurred.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 104.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' Thanks to the Ten-Lords Commission, being stricken with mara had long since become a terrifying but avoidable fate for Xianzhou natives... The puzzling thing is that despite the Commission's protection, we're now seeing an increase.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 105.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' More and more citizens &mdash; in particular those dealing with great risks and stress like the Cloud Knights &mdash; are becoming stricken with mara.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 106.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' Moreover, the mara-struck have taken on a horrifying appearance &mdash; as if they're turning into some sort of monster... This certainly differs from what I thought I knew about the illness.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So, you need me to eliminate the mara-struck?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202160011-->
:::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 107.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' We wouldn't have the audacity to trouble you with that &mdash; the general has a plan to suppress the illness.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you think there might be a hidden agenda at play?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202160013-->
:::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 108.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' That appears to be the case &mdash; no smoke without fire, as they say... Despite being just a servant of the Realm-Keeping Commission, spending a considerable amount of time on the front lines has sharpened my senses to potential dangers...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_202160014-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202160014-->
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 109.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' You're a capable person, and since the general entrusted you with locating the Stellaron, it's only a matter of time before you run into mara-struck...
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 110.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' If you come across any clues, remember to inform the Realm-Keeping Commission straight away. My colleagues and I will handle any situation with haste and to the best of our ability.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 dahao 111.ogg}} '''Dahao:''' Speaking of which, have you made any discoveries so far?
