::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502020104: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502020104.json-->
::'''Dahao:''' Thanks to you, we aren't as busy as before. However, as the Realm-Keeping Commission manages basically everything in both the sky and the world, we can never be idle.
::'''Dahao:''' Organizing post-disaster reconstruction, pursuing the Sanctus Medicus remnants, and arresting looters... Alas, there is plenty of work to be done despite the disaster being over...
::'''Dahao:''' The good thing is that Jingyan is very capable, and Songyan is... doing okay. Thanks to their help, I'm not overwhelmed by the workload.
::'''Dahao:''' I think I'll need a lot more help from you in the future... Don't turn me down when the time comes. Let me thank you in advance.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502020104-->
